txt.en: Thank you for contributing your collection! Please place your items in the box to receive your reward.
Wanted: Blackened sword sheaths from the Orcs near Trestlebridge. Deliver the items to Guardsman Otley in the town of Trestlebridge.
'We will be able to refit these for our weapons quickly. Thank you.'
'Part vengeance and part necessity, we need the sword sheaths from the Orcs. We need to protect the weapons that we have.'
DNT HIDING CONTENT - Task: Blackened Sword Sheaths
Guardsman Otley, in Trestlebridge, is awaiting delivery of blackened sword sheaths.
Deliver the blackened sword sheaths to Guardsman Otley at Trestlebridge
Wanted: Blackened sword sheaths from the Orcs near Trestlebridge.
